snippet.title: Die for Valhalla! – Release Date Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
In the land of Vikings a monstrous portal has opened. The Great Old One is plotting to take over the world. Chaos spreads far and wide... and the party's just getting started! Novice Valkyries along with their new mysterious friend set out to save the world. What could possibly go wrong?

Coming May 29th to PS4™!
